                  </app>
                  <app loc="9">
                     <lem>kālvakoṇḍa</lem>
                     <note>There may be a small and faint vowel mark (<foreign>e</foreign> or <foreign>i</foreign>) on top of the regularly formed <foreign>l</foreign>. In l19, <foreign>le</foreign> in <foreign>kule</foreign> is cursive, without a separate vowel mark on top.</note>
                  </app>
                  <app loc="13">
                     <lem>°śarmmabhyāṁ</lem>
